  <entry>
    <title>使用Python批量处理工作表</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/2022/10/20/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Python%E6%89%B9%E9%87%8F%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E8%A1%A8/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/2022/10/20/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Python%E6%89%B9%E9%87%8F%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E8%A1%A8/</id>
    <published>2022-10-19T16:34:59.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-10-19T16:35:43.875Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="使用Python批量处理工作表"><a href="#使用Python批量处理工作表" class="headerlink" title="使用Python批量处理工作表"></a>使用Python批量处理工作表</h1><hr><h2 id="1、实现要求："><a href="#1、实现要求：" class="headerlink" title="1、实现要求："></a>1、实现要求：</h2><p><img lazyload="" alt="image" data-src="https://pic1.imgdb.cn/item/634faa0716f2c2beb13fe5ff.jpg"></p><hr><h2 id="2、配置要求："><a href="#2、配置要求：" class="headerlink" title="2、配置要求："></a>2、配置要求：</h2><blockquote><p>1、安装<strong>xlwt、xlrd</strong>库，指定版本为1.2.0，因为新版本不支持对xlsx进行操作</p><p>按住<strong>Win+R</strong>输入<strong>cmd</strong>进入终端，分别执行以下两个语句即可安装库</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pip install xlwt==1.2.0</span><br><span class="line">pip install xlrd==1.2.0</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure></blockquote><hr><h2 id="3、编写代码："><a href="#3、编写代码：" class="headerlink" title="3、编写代码："></a>3、编写代码：</h2><blockquote><blockquote><p>1、首先调用<strong>xlrd</strong>库打卡“复试名单.xlsx</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight python"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Book = xlrd.open_workbook(<span class="string">"复试名单.xlsx"</span>) <span class="comment"># 返回一个文件操作对象</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><blockquote><p>2、打开文件中的表格，并且打印下表格的行列数</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight python"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Sheet = Book.sheet_by_name(<span class="string">"公示"</span>)<span class="comment"># 打开公示表格，一个xlsx文件内可以有多个表格，因此要指定表格打开</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">"表有{}行、{}列"</span>.<span class="built_in">format</span>(Sheet.nrows, Sheet.ncols)) </span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><blockquote><p>3、读出所有学院并赋值给字典变量，利用字典变量不重复性来查看一共有多少个学院</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight python"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">CollegeName = <span class="built_in">set</span>(data.col_values(<span class="number">4</span>)[<span class="number">1</span>:]) <span class="comment"># 读取第4列，从第一行开始读，因为第一行是列属性</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><blockquote><p>4、封装一个创建文件和文件夹的函数</p><p>创建文件夹需要用到<strong>os</strong>库，该库为python自带库，不需要安装直接import即可</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight python"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">mkdir</span>(<span class="params">xlsxname</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    folder = os.getcwd()  <span class="comment"># 获取py文件绝对路径</span></span><br><span class="line">    filepath = folder + <span class="string">'\\'</span> + xlsxname  <span class="comment"># 获取当前py文件绝地路径并加上要创建的文件夹名称</span></span><br><span class="line">    d[xlsxname] = []   <span class="comment"># 为每个学院的值创建一个列表来存放数据</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> <span class="keyword">not</span> os.path.exists(filepath):   <span class="comment"># 判断文件夹是否已存在</span></span><br><span class="line">      os.mkdir(filepath)   <span class="comment"># 创建文件夹</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">else</span>:  </span><br><span class="line">      <span class="built_in">print</span>(xlsxname + <span class="string">" 文件夹已存在"</span>)  </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">try</span>:</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="built_in">open</span>(filepath + <span class="string">'\\'</span> + xlsxname + <span class="string">'.xlsx'</span>, <span class="string">'w'</span>).close()  <span class="comment"># 在文件夹内创建表格文件，已存在则覆盖</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">except</span> PermissionError:  <span class="comment"># 文件已被打开在用open打开文件会有PermissionError错误</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">"文件被占用，请先退出已打开的xlsx表格文件！"</span>)  </span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><blockquote><p>5、为所有学院分别创建一个文件夹，在文件夹内在创建一个学院名称.xlsx表格文件</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight python"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> CN <span class="keyword">in</span> CollegeName:  <span class="comment"># 为每个学院都创建一个文件夹和xlsx文件</span></span><br><span class="line">mkdir(CN)  <span class="comment"># 调用创建文件函数</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><blockquote><p>6、接下来将每个学院键的值即各自学院的学生数据写入相应的学院.xlsx文件中</p><p>封装一个xlsx写入函数，参数为所有学院数据的字典</p></blockquote> <figure class="highlight python"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">xlsx_write</span>(<span class="params">dic: <span class="built_in">dict</span></span>):</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">try</span>:</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> dic:  <span class="comment"># 遍历每个学院</span></span><br><span class="line">            han = <span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line">            filepath = folder + <span class="string">'\\'</span> + i + <span class="string">'\\'</span> + i + <span class="string">'.xlsx'</span>  <span class="comment"># 获取文件绝对路径</span></span><br><span class="line">            workbook = xlwt.Workbook(filepath)  <span class="comment"># 获取写入文件对象</span></span><br><span class="line">            w = workbook.add_sheet(i)   <span class="comment"># 获取文件对象中的名字为i的表格的对象</span></span><br><span class="line">            write_row(w, <span class="number">0</span>, title)  <span class="comment"># 在每个学院表格的第一含写入列属性</span></span><br><span class="line">            w.col(<span class="number">0</span>).width = <span class="number">20</span> * <span class="number">256</span>   <span class="comment"># 设置列的宽度，让数据显示更清楚</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">for</span> j <span class="keyword">in</span> dic.get(i):  <span class="comment"># 遍历每个学院的每一个学生数据</span></span><br><span class="line">                write_row(w, han, j)    <span class="comment"># 行内写入学生数据</span></span><br><span class="line">                han += <span class="number">1</span>  <span class="comment"># 行数加一</span></span><br><span class="line">            workbook.save(filepath)  <span class="comment"># 保存表格</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">except</span> PermissionError:  <span class="comment"># 文件被占用时会报错</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">"文件被占用，请先退出已打开的xlsx表格文件！"</span>)  </span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure></blockquote><hr><h1 id="至此Python批量处理工作表程序就写完啦！"><a href="#至此Python批量处理工作表程序就写完啦！" class="headerlink" title="至此Python批量处理工作表程序就写完啦！"></a>至此Python批量处理工作表程序就写完啦！</h1><h3 id="源代码以及”复试名单-xlsx”文件可以点击-链接-进行下载"><a href="#源代码以及”复试名单-xlsx”文件可以点击-链接-进行下载" class="headerlink" title="源代码以及”复试名单.xlsx”文件可以点击 链接 进行下载"></a>源代码以及”复试名单.xlsx”文件可以点击 <strong><a class="link" href="https://wwm.lanzoux.com/iUn7u0e7srsf">链接<i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i></a></strong> 进行下载</h3><p>有问题欢迎在下面进行评论噢，看到就会回复您！</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
